    highlight: "Led team of 12 product managers, marketers, and analysts. Owned product vision for advertiser reporting console and smart creative versioning. Defined PRDs for OLAP-based analytics enabling performance analysis across placements, audiences, and messaging.",
    metrics: [
      { value: "12", label: "Team Members Led" }
